  <bioghist id="aspace_23147669ebcbef5d94e57cb4b9fba19c">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Formerly the Department of Textiles and Apparel in the College of Human Ecology, in 2007 it changed its name to the Department of Fiber Science and Apparel Design. In 2021 the Department of Design and Environmental Analysis and the Department of Fiber Science and Apparel Design combined to become the Department of Human Centered Design.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_efc2a507d649c63736c1486969254bc5">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes, posters, brochures, faculty annual reports, publications, and DVD of 2007 design league fashion show.</p>  </scopecontent>
